# 🏗️ Project Architecture

```
                Source Folder
                     │
         ┌───────────┴───────────┐
         │                       │
         ▼                       ▼
   Read File Data         Generate Header
         │                       │
         └───────────┬───────────┘
                     ▼
             XOR Encryption
                     │
                     ▼
              Packed Archive
                     │
      ─────────────────────────────────
                     │
                     ▼
             Read Archive
                     │
             Parse Header
                     │
             XOR Decryption
                     │
                     ▼
           Restored Original Files
```

