---

# 📋 How to Run

## Compile

```bash
javac Packer.java
javac Unpacker.java
```

---

## Run Packer

```bash
java program606
```

Example

```
Enter the name of folder :
Documents

Enter the name of packed file :
Archive.pack
```

---

## Run Unpacker

```bash
java program614
```

Example

```
Enter the name of packed file :
Archive.pack
```

The original files will be recreated automatically.

---

# 📊 Workflow

```
Folder
   │
   ▼
Read Files
   │
Generate Header
   │
Encrypt Data
   │
Create Archive
   │
──────────────
   │
Read Archive
   │
Read Header
   │
Decrypt Data
   │
Restore Files
```

