---

# 📈 Advantages

- Lightweight implementation
- Easy to understand
- Demonstrates core operating system and file handling concepts
- No external libraries required
- Simple encryption mechanism
- Efficient binary storage format

---

# ⚠️ Limitations

- Currently packs only `.txt` files
- Uses fixed XOR key (not suitable for production security)
- No file compression
- No password authentication
- Flat folder structure only
- Limited archive metadata

